Interface DirectedRelationshipPropertyPath

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Allocate, Copy, DeriveReqt, Refine, Satisfy, Trace, Verify
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AllocateImpl, CopyImpl, DeriveReqtImpl, DirectedRelationshipPropertyPathImpl, RefineImpl, SatisfyImpl, TraceImpl, VerifyImpl

    public interface DirectedRelationshipPropertyPath
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Directed Relationship Property Path'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Directed Relationship
    • Source Context
    • Source Property Path
    • Target Context
    • Target Property Path
    See Also:
    BlocksPackage.getDirectedRelationshipPropertyPath()
